{"id": "1251628015671050250", "channel_id": "1251628015671050250", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```　　在深海界域的所有半魚形喚醒體中，即使是一米八的歐魯加也算是他們之中的矮個子。他能勉為其難地舉起對同體型而言大小正好的魚叉與刀劍，卻連人類調查員也可以擊倒他，甚至論游泳能力，都難以相信他與深海之力有什麼連結。\n　　但小心了，那遠古民族的血性並沒有因為他的孱弱而減少。兵器無法支持他戰勝，於是他學會了陷阱；身手不能比拚其他人，於是他學會了狡計。非利士人想要什麼，從來不會禮貌的詢問你，而是強取豪奪。```\n\n跟前面幾個孩子比起來，這就是我在YY鯊魚的好基友而已，所以機制也沒有前幾位那樣認真<:1nekotiredempty_kitty:1206774459181305956> \n\nP1 的角色圖來自 [XxZariuWolf](https://twitter.com/XxZariuWolf/status/1257806778454224900)\nP3 的ICON來自 [這裡](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/sunset_905119?term=sea+sun&page=1&position=31&origin=search&related_id=905119)\n\n＞＞＞前作\n⁠https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1229156600737042483\nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1240360398876573787\nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1241149966861209600/1241149966861209600", "timestamp": "2024-06-15T20:02:53.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-15T20:04:29.101000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🐋", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [{"id": "1251628015943811208", "filename": "873c37ed6773c80b.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 74032, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1251628015671050250/1251628015943811208/873c37ed6773c80b.png?ex=69faf5ad&is=69f9a42d&hm=e2f9951e3fc69c464d6782cb24e5803661193b6bc5337aa05770498792ac4357&"}, {"id": "1251628016279490600", "filename": "d33062534772bcd8.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 273423, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1251628015671050250/1251628016279490600/d33062534772bcd8.png?ex=69faf5ad&is=69f9a42d&hm=7d6c1cb213f3939d2330c7d149b0b950307f1841118af8bce3d3b3be16d4d489&"}, {"id": "1251628016585408615", "filename": "0a92cafbc27ad326.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 196772, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1251628015671050250/1251628016585408615/0a92cafbc27ad326.png?ex=